# Setting up tRPC

Primary reference: `skills/setting-up-trpc/SKILL.md`

Use this rule for:

- tRPC v11 + TanStack Query install and pin
- `src/server/trpc.ts` (init, context with Auth.js v5 session, `protectedProcedure` middleware)
- `src/server/router.ts` (root router; split into `routers/<module>.ts` as it grows)
- `src/pages/api/trpc/[trpc].ts` (the only catch-all tRPC handler)
- `src/lib/trpc.ts` (typed client, SPA mode `ssr: false`, `httpBatchLink`)
- `_app.tsx` wrapped with `trpc.withTRPC(App)`
- Zod input validation on every procedure
- Refusal to add new raw `pages/api/*` handlers for app data
